  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  1) Males or females age 13 to 22 years.&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  2) Overweight or obese (BMI ≥85th percentile for age/sex, or ≥25 kg/m2 for&#xD;
             participants ≥18 years)&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  3) Diagnosis with prediabetes or type 2 diabetes&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  4) Consent (subjects 18 and older), Parental/guardian permission (subjects 13-17),&#xD;
             assent (subjects 13-17)&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  5) Willingness to wear Fitbit during waking hours daily for duration of run-in and&#xD;
             intervention.&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  6) Possession of a smartphone.&#xD;
&#xD;
        Exclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  1) Potential subject unable to speak or read in English&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  2) Severe cognitive impairment&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  3) Permanent or temporary physical disability that impairs ambulation or precludes&#xD;
             engagement in MVPA&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  4) Current pregnancy&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  5) Previously-diagnosed or current restrictive or purging eating disorder&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  6) Moderate to vigorous physical activity (MVPA) &gt;30 minutes per day or Fitbit wear &lt;&#xD;
             4 days during second week of 2-week run-in period&#xD;
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
